1. US Vice President Vance will deliver a speech at the Bitcoin 2025 Conference;
2. Analysts have mixed opinions on Coinbase's acquisition of Deribit: derivatives expansion is optimistic, retail growth is questionable;
3. Irish mixed martial arts star Conor McGregor calls on the country to establish a strategic Bitcoin reserve;
4. The Indonesian government may require Worldcoin to delete 500,000 retinal data;
5. Cointelegraph's official account is suspected to have been stolen, please be vigilant;
6. Coinbase CEO: Considered adopting Michael Saylor's Bitcoin investment strategy, but ultimately did not adopt it because the risk was too high;
7. Optimism: The Isthmus hard fork has been activated, and the Ethereum Pectra upgrade will be introduced to Superchain.
